abstract.text: This class represents a Display Rule, a MapsIndoors concept which describes a number of styling values for MapsIndoors objects.
The values contained within dictates how the MapsIndoors SDK renders a given object on the map (POI, area, selection, model, etc.).

inlineContent.text: Display Rule data can be edited through the MapsIndoors CMS, and can be modified at runtime in SDKs. Invoke
to reset all values to those from the CMS.

This class represents a Display Rule, a MapsIndoors concept which describes a number of styling values for MapsIndoors objects.
The values contained within dictates how the MapsIndoors SDK renders a given object on the map (POI, area, selection, model, etc.).
